In `@lib/pages/hitokoto_settings_page.dart` around lines 61 - 67, The
_hasApiNinjasApiKey flag is only loaded in initState, so switching to API Ninjas
via _saveSelectedProvider doesn't refresh the card subtitle; after calling
context.read<SettingsService>().setDailyQuoteProvider(provider) in
_saveSelectedProvider, query the SettingsService for the current API Ninjas key
presence (or the raw key) and update _hasApiNinjasApiKey inside setState (or
call a small helper like _updateApiNinjasKeyStatus that reads the service and
sets _hasApiNinjasApiKey); ensure this helper is also invoked whenever the
selected provider changes so the UI reflects the actual key state immediately.
```

